author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Moneysupermarket.Com Group Posts FY ‍Operating Profit Of 94.9 Mln STG
text:
Feb 22 (Reuters) - Moneysupermarket.Com Group Plc:
* FY ‍OPERATING PROFIT £94.9M VERSUS £91.1M YEAR BEFORE​ * ‍FY ADJUSTED EPS 16.9P VERSUS 15.7P​ * ‍FY ORDINARY DIVIDEND FOR YEAR 10.44P VERSUS 9.85P ​ * CORE MARKETS EXPECTED TO GROW AT AROUND 6-7%​, FORECAST GROWTH TO BE SLOWER THAN THAT IN 2018​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
